    <div class="cbox-10-0 p_item"><div class="e_image-11 s_img">
                    <a href="/Products_details_1/93.html" target="_self">
                    <img src="https://omo-oss-image.thefastimg.com/portal-saas/pg2025101513031865997/cms/image/4ae15688-8eda-449a-9744-4b84b4f1e503.png" alt="铝电解槽双端节能技术及工业系统" title="铝电解槽双端节能技术及工业系统" la="la" needthumb="true"/>
                    </a>
</div><div class="e_container-12 s_layout">
    <div class="cbox-12-0 p_item"><p class="e_text-15 s_title">
        <a href="/Products_details_1/93.html" target="_self">
        铝电解槽双端节能技术及工业系统
        </a>
</p><div class="e_richText-25 s_title clearfix">
    根据流程工程学原理，独创了通过构建铝电解热特性与热流分布的“流程网络”，实现铝电解流程系统温度特性、炉帮调节与槽侧壁散热之间的非线性“耦合”，从而构建合理的“耗散”结构，使“能量流”在动态有序运行过程中实现耗散“最小化”。
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
          <div class="cbox-9 swiper-slide" saf-link="">
          <div class="e_container-10 s_layout">
    <div class="cbox-10-0 p_item"><div class="e_image-11 s_img">
                    <a href="/Products_details_1/98.html" target="_self">
                    <img src="https://omo-oss-image.thefastimg.com/portal-saas/pg2025101513031865997/cms/image/df62b770-ad71-4043-b249-7bfd1323200e.jpg" alt="铝电解槽应急短接与停槽节能技术" title="铝电解槽应急短接与停槽节能技术" la="la" needthumb="true"/>
                    </a>
</div><div class="e_container-12 s_layout">
    <div class="cbox-12-0 p_item"><p class="e_text-15 s_title">
        <a href="/Products_details_1/98.html" target="_self">
        铝电解槽应急短接与停槽节能技术
        </a>
</p><div class="e_richText-25 s_title clearfix">
    使用停槽短接节能技术，单槽降低短接母线压降30mV 以上，折合吨铝节电5~8kWh。
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
          <div class="cbox-9 swiper-slide" saf-link="">
          <div class="e_container-10 s_layout">
    <div class="cbox-10-0 p_item"><div class="e_image-11 s_img">
                    <a href="/Products_details_1/107.html" target="_self">
