                    </a>
</div><div class="e_container-12 s_layout">
    <div class="cbox-12-0 p_item"><p class="e_text-15 s_title">
        <a href="/Products_details_1/107.html" target="_self">
        固定炉（20T~100T)
        </a>
</p><div class="e_richText-25 s_title clearfix">
    适用范围：各种铝加工熔炼保温场景。目前业绩160台套。
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
          <div class="cbox-9 swiper-slide" saf-link="">
